title: The Marine (John Cena)
description: WWWE Champion John Cena is marine John Triton, when his wife is kidnapped he will do anything to find her and bring her home safely and god help the man who has taken her!!!  What follows is an action-packed chase with brutal fights that will make your heart pound. Also stars Robert Patrick (liquid metal man from Terminator 2 and John Doggett from The X Files)
